---
import Share from "~components/ux/Share.astro";
import BaseLayout from "~layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

---
<BaseLayout title="Igbo Restoration Project" >
    <section id="share-linkcast" class="aspect-video bg-cover bg-center w-full min-h-screen flex justify-center items-center pb-4 bg-black/80" style="background-image: url('https://source.unsplash.com/random?igbo');">
        <div class="h-full">
            <!--Nav-->
            <div class="w-full mx-auto">
                <div class="w-full flex items-center justify-between backdrop-brightness-50 backdrop-blur px-8">
                    <a class="flex items-center text-red-300 drop-shadow-md no-underline hover:no-underline font-bold text-2xl lg:text-4xl" href="#">
                        Igbo<span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-red-300 via-red-400 to-red-500"> Restoration</span><span class="text-white">.org</span>
                    </a>

                    <div class="flex w-1/2 justify-end content-center">
                        <a class="inline-block drop-shadow-sm text-white no-underline hover:text-red-500 hover:text-underline text-center h-10 p-2 md:h-auto md:p-4 transform hover:scale-125 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=#">
                            <svg class="fill-current h-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                                <path
                                d="M30.063 7.313c-.813 1.125-1.75 2.125-2.875 2.938v.75c0 1.563-.188 3.125-.688 4.625a15.088 15.088 0 0 1-2.063 4.438c-.875 1.438-2 2.688-3.25 3.813a15.015 15.015 0 0 1-4.625 2.563c-1.813.688-3.75 1-5.75 1-3.25 0-6.188-.875-8.875-2.625.438.063.875.125 1.375.125 2.688 0 5.063-.875 7.188-2.5-1.25 0-2.375-.375-3.375-1.125s-1.688-1.688-2.063-2.875c.438.063.813.125 1.125.125.5 0 1-.063 1.5-.25-1.313-.25-2.438-.938-3.313-1.938a5.673 5.673 0 0 1-1.313-3.688v-.063c.813.438 1.688.688 2.625.688a5.228 5.228 0 0 1-1.875-2c-.5-.875-.688-1.813-.688-2.75 0-1.063.25-2.063.75-2.938 1.438 1.75 3.188 3.188 5.25 4.25s4.313 1.688 6.688 1.813a5.579 5.579 0 0 1 1.5-5.438c1.125-1.125 2.5-1.688 4.125-1.688s3.063.625 4.188 1.813a11.48 11.48 0 0 0 3.688-1.375c-.438 1.375-1.313 2.438-2.563 3.188 1.125-.125 2.188-.438 3.313-.875z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                        <a
                        class="inline-block text-white drop-shadow-sm no-underline hover:text-red-500 hover:text-underline text-center h-10 p-2 md:h-auto md:p-4 transform hover:scale-125 duration-300 ease-in-out"
                        href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=#"
                        >
                        <svg class="fill-current h-6" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
                            <path d="M19 6h5V0h-5c-3.86 0-7 3.14-7 7v3H8v6h4v16h6V16h5l1-6h-6V7c0-.542.458-1 1-1z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--Main-->
        <div class="container p-8 pt-24 md:pt-36 mx-auto flex flex-wrap flex-col portrait:flex-col-reverse landscape:md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
            <!--Left Col-->
            <div class="flex flex-col landscape:w-full landscape:xl:w-2/5 justify-center lg:items-start overflow-y-hidden backdrop-brightness-50 backdrop-blur p-8 rounded-md">
                <h1 class="my-4 text-3xl md:text-5xl text-white drop-shadow-sm font-bold leading-tight text-center md:text-left">
                    Nnọọ!
                    <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-red-300 via-red-400 to-red-500">
                        Igbo Restoration
                    </span>
                    website is launched!
                </h1>
                <p class="leading-normal text-white md:text-2xl mb-8 text-center md:text-left">
                    Want to stay updated? Please sign up for our newsletter or join our <a class="text-lime-300" title="Join our Whatsapp Group" href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/DZoimK4izJDAV9dZpPy2Qz">Whatsapp Group IRI</a>!
                </p>

                <form class="bg-red-700 w-full shadow-lg rounded-lg px-8 pt-6 pb-8 mb-4" netlify enctype="multipart/form-data"  data-netlify="true" data-netlify-honeypot="field-of-expertise" name="enyimba-aba-2024" method="POST">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-white py-2 font-bold mb-2" for="emailaddress">
                            Signup for our newsletter
                        </label>
                        <input
                        class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full p-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:ring transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out"
                        id="emailaddress"
                        name="emailaddress"
                        type="email"
                        placeholder="you@somewhere.com"
                        />
                        <input
                        class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full p-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:ring transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out hidden"
                        id="field-of-expertise"
                        name="field-of-expertise"
                        type="text"
                        placeholder="your occupation"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-4">
                        <button
                        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-red-100 hover:from-red-300 hover:to-red-400 hover:text-white text-red-700 font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded focus:ring transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out"
                        type="submit"
                        >Sign Up</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <!--Right Col-->
            <div class="w-full xl:w-3/5 p-12 overflow-hidden">

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto md:pt-16 lg:w-1/2">
            <div
            class="block rounded-lg bg-white drop-shadow-sm shadow-secondary-1 dark:bg-surface-dark mx-auto w-full md:w-4/5 transform -rotate-1 transition hover:scale-105 duration-700 ease-in-out hover:rotate-1">
            <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden bg-cover bg-no-repeat"
            data-twe-ripple-init
            data-twe-ripple-color="light">
            <img
            class="rounded-t-lg w-full"
            src="/images/igborestoration.jpg"
            alt="" />
            <a href="#!">
                <div
                class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 top-0 h-full w-full overflow-hidden bg-[hsla(0,0%,98%,0.15)] bg-fixed opacity-0 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:opacity-100"></div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 text-surface dark:text-white">
            <h5 class="mb-2 text-xl font-medium leading-tight">IGBO RESTORATION INITIATIVES (IRI)</h5>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                Greetings to Umu Ndi-Gbo. Udo'nu!
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                Granted, quite a lot of our original Igbo heritages were either disfigured, destroyed, plagiarised, whitewashed or completely changed.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                From our True Igbo Histories to our Igbo Lunar Calendar; to Igbo CULTure (Odi'n'Ala); to Igbo Family structure; to Igbo spiritualities (Nso'Ala, Iwu'Ala and Ntu'Ala); to the rightful position of Igbo women in Igbo societies; from Igbo language to Igbo dressings ,(Ishi Agu vs Ishi Odum), Traditional Igbo foods and drinks, Nka'n'Uzu Igbo, Igbo Village Waters and Ancient Igbo Agriculture.
                Indeed, lot of damages have been done against our precious Igboness by our enslavers and colonists.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                The time to restore the glories and greatness of Igbo people and their natural endowments and heritages is now.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                Igbo Restoration Initiatives (IRI) was established to practically tackle and restore all that made us Igbo people.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                Welcome Igbo Restoration Initiatives (IRI) with change in focus.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base">
                Signed<br />
                IRI Board of Directors.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--Footer-->
</div>
</div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>